data.description: Dueno a Dueno - Seller Finance Only.  Discover the epitome of modern living in this meticulously crafted single-story home built by LGI Homes in 2020. Nestled in the coveted Preserve at Medina Subdivision, this property offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style. Welcome to 15246 Walcott Ridge, your dream home awaits!    *Bedrooms: 3 spacious bedrooms provide ample space for relaxation and privacy.  *Bathrooms: 2 well-appointed bathrooms, including a master en-suite, offer convenience and luxury.  *Garage: A generous 2-car garage with space for storage.  *Open Concept: The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it ideal for entertaining.  *Modern Kitchen: The chef's kitchen is adorned with sleek countertops, contemporary cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances.  * Backyard Retreat: Enjoy your morning coffee or host barbecues in the nice-sized backyard, a canvas for your outdoor vision.  * Location: Minutes away from major highways and the Toyota Power Plant, providing easy access to work and play.  * Community: The Preserve at Medina Subdivision offers a family-friendly atmosphere and community amenities.  * Energy-Efficient: Designed with energy efficiency in mind, saving you money while being environmentally conscious.  This home represents a rare opportunity to own a modern, move-in-ready property in the thriving Von Ormy area. Whether you're a first-time buyer, a growing family, or looking for the perfect retirement retreat, 15246 Walcott Ridge caters to all lifestyles.  Convenience meets comfort in this LGI Homes masterpiece. Don't miss your chance to call this gem your own. Schedule a viewing today and envision your future in this splendid home.  Reach out right away to inquiries or to arrange a showing.
